metadata.name: The fragrance of a dead Rose
metadata.description:
"The fragrance of a dead Rose" is a story derived and inspired by the words of Emily Dickinson. Her story and words around death comforted me to look around and get inspired to define a path where energy is passed to an immortal realm. 

This is also my genesis edition work on my smart contract. I hope this piece gives you meaning and defines a conversation we ignore at times. Remember this is not just a beautiful frame but a meaning that can be defined by many as you collect. 

Much love,  
Fawkes
